  "page": "Vaes Leisi",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Essos.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Vaes Leisi is located in Essos\"><img alt=\"Vaes Leisi is located in Essos\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/300px-Essos.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"284\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/450px-Essos.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/600px-Essos.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 27.2%; left: 79.2%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Vaes Leisi\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: -6.5em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Vaes Leisi</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\"><a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> west of the <a href=\"/index.php/Bone_Mountains\" title=\"Bone Mountains\">Bone Mountains</a> and the location of Vaes Leisi\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Vaes Leisi</b> is a ruined settlement in the forests of northern <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>. It is located in the western <a href=\"/index.php/Kingdom_of_the_Ifequevron\" title=\"Kingdom of the Ifequevron\">Kingdom of the Ifequevron</a> on a small peninsula jutting into the <a href=\"/index.php/Shivering_Sea\" title=\"Shivering Sea\">Shivering Sea</a>. East of Vaes Leisi are <a href=\"/index.php/New_Ibbish\" title=\"New Ibbish\">New Ibbish</a> and the ruins of <a href=\"/index.php/Vaes_Aresak\" title=\"Vaes Aresak\">Vaes Aresak</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiaf_the_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiaf_the_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vaes_Leisi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Vaes Leisi is a <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_language\" title=\"Dothraki language\">Dothraki language</a> name, meaning \"City of Ghosts\". Consisting of carved trees and haunted grottoes, the settlement was inhabited by a vanished people the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> called the <a href=\"/index.php/Ifequevron\" title=\"Ifequevron\">Ifequevron</a>, or \"<a href=\"/index.php/Woods_walkers\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Woods walkers\">woods walkers</a>\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_vaes_leisi.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_vaes_leisi.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vaes_Leisi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiaf_the_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiaf_the_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  The Known World.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiaf_vaes_leisi.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiaf_vaes_leisi.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  Vaes Leisi.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403092656\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.035 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.038 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 692/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12292/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3570/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1626/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1062/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   27.099      1 -total\n 64.14%   17.381      1 Template:Location_map\n 60.95%   16.517      1 Template:Location_map+\n 50.05%   13.563      1 Template:Location_map~\n 27.40%    7.426      2 Template:Ref\n 19.27%    5.222     22 Template:Location_map_Essos\n 16.21%    4.392      2 Template:Ref/core\n 10.49%    2.843      3 Template:Location_map/decdeg\n  7.32%    1.984      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:14243-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403092655 and revision id 211401\n -->\n",
